    <description>
LightCrosshair is a lightweight, high-performance crosshair overlay for competitive gaming on Windows 10/11.

## Features
- Custom crosshair builder with full shape control
- Integrated FPS overlay with ETW/PresentMon anti-cheat safe telemetry
- Process-aware display color management (per-profile gamma/contrast/brightness)
- Modern profile workflow with immutable defaults
- Low CPU footprint optimized for gameplay
- Multi-monitor support with DPI awareness
- Screen recording detection for streaming/recording

## Requirements
- Windows 10 or later
- .NET 8.0 Runtime (automatically installed if needed)

## Installation
Simply run: `choco install lightcrosshair`

After installation, launch LightCrosshair from your Start Menu or find the executable in Program Files.
    </description>
    <summary>Lightweight gaming crosshair overlay with FPS counter and color management</summary>
