v1.3.0 (May 2026): Portable standalone release, improved shutdown stability, fixed visibility-toggle FPS tracking regressions, refined process-targeted display color automation, and updated default hotkeys.

See https://github.com/PrimeBuild-pc/LightCrosshair/releases for full details.
